---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Your Name">
  <h1>Hello, I'm Your Name</h1>

  <!-- 🔧 Replace all of this with your own intro -->
  <div class="intro">
    <p>
      I'm a software engineer based in <strong>Bengaluru</strong>. I write about
      software, building things from scratch, and whatever I'm currently obsessed with.
    </p>
    <p>
      I work on <a href="#">interesting problem here</a>. Before that, I studied
      computer science at <a href="#">University Name</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      I've written <a href="/articles">a few articles</a> on topics I care about,
      and you can see some of my personal <a href="/projects">projects here</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of work I enjoy reading, coffee, and spending too much time on
      side projects that may or may not ever ship.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h3>Recently</h3>
    <p>
      <!-- 🔧 A short, casual "what I'm up to" section works well here -->
      Currently exploring systems programming and writing about what I learn.
      Also trying to get better at badminton.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>
      <!-- 🔧 Replace with your email or contact method -->
      Best way to reach me is by email at <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a>.
      I try to reply to everyone.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
